screenshot(1)

# NAME

screenshot - Take a screenshot of a region

# SYNOPSIS

screenshot

# DESCRIPTION

Open screen overlay to select a region to screenshot. The image is saved in the
Desktop folder.

# OPTIONS

None

# OPERANDS

None

# ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES

None

# FILES

_$HOME/Desktop_
	Target directory to contain the images

# DEPENDENCIES

- grim
- slurp
